result.description:
The EPIC Consortium will prepare a dissemination and exploitation plan related to the planned Centre of Excellence containing the following elements (synchronized with relevant WP2 tasks):
•	Identification and classification of target stakeholders to be addressed;
•	The dissemination methods and their specific associated activities, respectively sustainability actions;
•	Schedule and complementarily of the dissemination activities among partners;
•	Individual dissemination and exploitation plans.
